&gt; Be careful of assigning any type of class to different voice types. Just because a voice might sound low and growly does not mean it is a lower life form. If we hear a spirit voice that sounds week and feint, we think the spirit is in pain or trouble. But that isn&#39;t necessarily the case. It could be that is all it could do at the moment due to any number of inhibiting factors.. Breaking the dimensional barrier is probably not easy.
